  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/c78e265b4912f782e614835438ccf939.avif?t=1769399032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras_big/c78e265b4912f782e614835438ccf939.avif?t=1769399032 width=800 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/be04be95b814374cd7ad4122c3bcf57d.avif?t=1769399032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras_big/be04be95b814374cd7ad4122c3bcf57d.avif?t=1769399032 width=800 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A surreal psychological horror short visual novel where YOU are the protagonist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, a mysterious girl suddenly appears in the protagonist's room...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your task is simple: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/89f29dc6677c4a99148645e0a6a5c436.avif?t=1769399032\" width=128 height=99 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Say hello to the girl~</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through hundreds of choices to respond to \"the girl's existence.\"</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the essence of \"being\" and uncover the truth of this \"world.\"</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And your mission is even simpler: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/4fe1586b00b0336a2a4e6579a7c02313.avif?t=1769399032\" width=128 height=99 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Say hello to the girl~</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As king, listen to your subjects' counsel, especially those \"loyal ministers.\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make strawberry cake, eat the cake, eat the cake - will you really let her eat the cake?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stop FONTAINEBLEAU's plot! Don't hand over the time machine!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey to the Silvery Forest, defeat the Demon Lord, fulfill the Dreamer's mission.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Date the mysterious girl at the world's end.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take some pills, have a heart-to-heart chat with them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witness your ending with the girl.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/e6ebac8404189237e0d8dfee8a854422.avif?t=1769399032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras_big/e6ebac8404189237e0d8dfee8a854422.avif?t=1769399032 width=800 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/98bc6a528dcae3589588b88897e81a84.avif?t=1769399032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras_big/98bc6a528dcae3589588b88897e81a84.avif?t=1769399032 width=800 height=516 /></span>There's no character introduction here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Rather than define myself with labels, I'd prefer we understand each other through shared experiences and memories.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You exist because you're you. I exist because I'm me. And here we are, meeting in this moment……</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Of course, how you interpret these words, how you perceive me... isn't that itself my \"self-introduction\"?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/48ce6b4a68856c2b435fdb99a188ea63.avif?t=1769399032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras_big/48ce6b4a68856c2b435fdb99a188ea63.avif?t=1769399032 width=800 height=412 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Small in stature, always smiling. </i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A mandrake researcher who loves writing visual novel scripts.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/ff86a82c9a5df3d68f505bd33d20e829.avif?t=1769399032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras_big/ff86a82c9a5df3d68f505bd33d20e829.avif?t=1769399032 width=800 height=412 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Tall and quiet.</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Rhythm games Master but ↑↑↓↓←→←→BA(⁎˃ᴗ˂⁎)!</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Of course, perhaps none of that matters most. What matters is...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>I hope you enjoy our time together.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/d8f4555cde967ddca46122fbcc7095d1.avif?t=1769399032\" width=128 height=99 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game welcomes live streaming (including monetized streams)~</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please include a link to the Steam page of <i>\"The NOexistenceN of you AND me\"</i> in the description of your stream, or introduce the game during the stream.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/c78e265b4912f782e614835438ccf939.avif?t=1769399032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras_big/c78e265b4912f782e614835438ccf939.avif?t=1769399032 width=800 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/be04be95b814374cd7ad4122c3bcf57d.avif?t=1769399032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras_big/be04be95b814374cd7ad4122c3bcf57d.avif?t=1769399032 width=800 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A surreal psychological horror short visual novel where YOU are the protagonist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, a mysterious girl suddenly appears in the protagonist's room...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your task is simple: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/89f29dc6677c4a99148645e0a6a5c436.avif?t=1769399032\" width=128 height=99 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Say hello to the girl~</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through hundreds of choices to respond to \"the girl's existence.\"</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the essence of \"being\" and uncover the truth of this \"world.\"</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And your mission is even simpler: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873080/extras/4fe1586b00b0336a2a4e6579a7c02313.avif?t=176